Waunakee's Drywall & Painting Experts Since 1998

Since 1998, First Choice Drywall has been providing the skill and efficiency required to keep projects moving without sacrificing quality, ensuring on-time completion and far fewer problems on the back end.

Whether you’re creating a custom home, small tract development, master-planned community or a commercial project, you can rely on First Choice Drywall’s years of experience as drywall and painting contractors to deliver a complete package of performance and accountability.

We provide a wide array of drywall and painting services including: new construction installations, home remodeling, drywall contracting, drywall repairs, full-service painting, staining and varnishing and more.

We service the greater Madison and Milwaukee area. Call 608-849-3018 to get your free estimate today.
